<!doctype html>  -->it shows that it is a html document.
<html>  --> it is a starting tag.
</html> --> it is ending tag.
there is two basic sections
1)<head>---</head >  head of the document.
2)<body>...</body>   body of the document.
😊tags inside the head.

<title>---</title>--- title of the website
meta tag-->it is basically that define information about our file
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="description" content ="this is awesome".

it says that the document has this kind of character set,it is a description for the website.

😊other tags inside body tag.

* <p>--</p> paragraph tag.
we can enter the content inside the body.
* <h1>--</h1> upto h6 is available.
which differs in size.
<b>--</b> --bold tag
<i>--</i> --italic tag
we can give both the same time.
<br>--</br>--create a new line in a html document.
<hr/>--it is a single tag.break up with horizontal line.
<big>--</big>  anything inside the tag is will appear as big.
<small>--</small>-- anything  inside the tag will appear as small.
<p>H<sub>2</sub>0</p>--it will give  H2O --2 will appear in the base...bcse of sub tag.
<p>10<sup>2</sup></p>--result is 10 square.
<!--sd,asfuefxcbnsd--> it is a comments tag.
<p style="colour: blue;">-- changing the colour.
<p style="color: blue; background-color: blue;">
<body style="color: blue; background-color: blue;">-- entire body will appear blue color.  

